:1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T15:14:32.000Z","msg":"精讀金句：如果條仔/女係要偷食，你點都左唔到佢<br />\n<br />\n所以我都係抱住平常心同信任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aff463e57fd7bf3055883a464a67a333ac0ffc82","tid":775451,"uid":2479,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"09f0b095f255eaddd9138c46f967236b3a27b0f4","tid":775451,"uid":199992,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bf45b89c937f909baeac7b540d07f920d50a1500","tid":775451,"uid":43289,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T09:45:03.000Z","msg":"以為自己開po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T10:16:36.000Z","msg":"絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知點算好 其實係怕講出黎之後佢會覺得我想局限佢社交圈子覺得我任性"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T15:31:59.000Z","msg":"其實我明你 因為我曾經都係咁嘅人<br />\n我另一半又係好易同女仔frd嘅人<br />\n但你唔同佢講你依家嘅感受 佢又點知呢<br />\n佢可能會做其他嘢增加返你嘅安全感<br />\n或者係佢自己都會自覺少啲同女仔有做嘢以外嘅接觸 除非佢哋係朋友<br />\n<br />\n但你都要明白 返學返工點都會有異性嘅存在 <br />\n我以前曾經好易呷醋 好易介意<br />\n但可能人長大咗 或者曾經為依樣嘢傾過 我依家都覺得生活中有異性嘅出現其實好正常<br />\n最緊要係我信佢對其他人無嘢 <br />\n<br />\n不過依啲都要啲時間去變<br />\n但如果你覺得你未必做到嘅話 我相信依個世界點都會有一個人係喺依方面同你夾得嚟<br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cec2e2041ee9ea83392380c3bbd8b6967e1ac797","tid":775451,"uid":199992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aff463e57fd7bf3055883a464a67a333ac0ffc82","tid":775451,"uid":2479,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"09f0b095f255eaddd9138c46f967236b3a27b0f4","tid":775451,"uid":199992,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bf45b89c937f909baeac7b540d07f920d50a1500","tid":775451,"uid":43289,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20